name: Zen Agenda. Scene 2.
description:
In a moment of pure, raw experience, the intrepid come over the crest of the hill. There they witnessed yet another astonishing occurrence. After what seemed an eternity of arduous trekking through volatile and noxious realms, those that remain have arrived. Whether or not the colossal vibrating beings they’re confronted with are benevolent is anyone’s guess. Some form of shelter, some kind of change is desperately needed. The first few, the bravest of the brave, take the leap and go with what’s in the air. 

2000 x 1200 300p
